Hey there,

Eric from Firecrawl here. We just shipped v2.5 and I'm really excited to sh=
are we're now the highest quality Web Data API on the market.

We built our own custom browser stack that automatically detects how pages =
are rendered and converts everything (PDFs, paginated tables, whatever) int=
o clean, agent-ready formats. This lets us index complete pages, not partia=
l snapshots, which is why our quality benchmarks are the highest.

We also built a semantic index that already serves 40% of all API calls. It=
 stores full page snapshots + embeddings + metadata for blazing fast data d=
elivery across most websites.

Check out the benchmarks and technical deep dive blog post here ( https://w=
ww.firecrawl.dev/blog/the-worlds-best-web-data-api-v25 ) and stay tuned, we=
're open sourcing our benchmarks soon!

Best,
Eric
